source.name: NOLA City Council Districts maps - 8.5 x 11
source.description: City of New Orleans, Council Districts.  PDF binder containing individual 8.5 x 11 (letter size) maps for each of the five New Orleans City Council Districts.  Update: As Needed.  Individual poster size maps (ANSI-E, 34 x 44) are available in PDF format for each of the Council Districts.
